  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: ec9a774f1c3f94c5ab3b77c67ac7f734, type: 3}
  m_Name: LoopReflect_05
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ReflectBranch
  lines:
  - I am officially stuck in a loop.
  - So how do I get out of this?
  - Maybe this is the universe helping me out in some #$@!*% up way?
  - I get unlimited tries at asking Daisy to the dance?
  - "If I ask her, maybe I\u2019ll stop looping?"
  - "That\u2019s not the craziest theory I could think of\u2026."
  - So then how do I actually ask her?
  - "Well asking her to the dance has been absolutely terrifying\u2026"
  - No matter how many times I try.
  - "So I think\u2026 I just need to get my confidence up?"
  - "Really get in a good conversation with her\u2026"
  - "So that the dread of asking her to the dance doesn\u2019t kill me\u2026."
  - "Again\u2026"
  - "Yep, let\u2019s go with that."
  - Alrighty then - what else can I say to her?
  commitLines: []
  isScripted: 1
